casebody.data:
October 14, 1963. No. 520,

October Term, 1962.

Chamberlin et al. v. Dade County Board of Public Instruction et al., E. F. P. Brigham on the motions.

374 U. S. 487. The motion of the intervening appellees to dispense with printing the motion to vacate the judgment is granted. The motion of intervening appellees to vacate the judgment is denied.
